messages.content: What is ComfyUI DPM++ 2M Alt Sampler?
ComfyUI DPM++ 2M Alt Sampler is a custom node or plugin for the ComfyUI GUI that uses a stable diffusion model to generate images and videos. It is based on the sampler introduced by hallatore.
Who introduced the sampler used in ComfyUI DPM++ 2M Alt Sampler?
The sampler used in ComfyUI DPM++ 2M Alt Sampler was introduced by hallatore.
What is the source code of ComfyUI DPM++ 2M Alt Sampler extracted from?
The source code of ComfyUI DPM++ 2M Alt Sampler is extracted from smZNodes, a repository by shiimizu.
Who is the author of the smZNodes repository?
shiimizu is the author of the smZNodes repository, from which the source code of ComfyUI DPM++ 2M Alt Sampler is extracted.
